I still want to live a normal life.

50
00:03:12,070 --> 00:03:13,760
But I think it's not easy anymore.

51
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,650
Anyways, just go to sleep first.

52
00:03:17,250 --> 00:03:18,780
Be sure to take your medicine.

53
00:03:19,300 --> 00:03:20,210
You must.

54
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,320
Okay.

55
00:03:22,650 --> 00:03:23,720
I'm hanging up.

56
00:03:23,720 --> 00:03:25,500
Hey, this guy started it again.

57
00:03:25,500 --> 00:03:26,780
Way back then,

58
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:29,300
