59
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:30,960
...and said, "I'm going to the military".

60
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,340
It's over just by saying it,

61
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:33,250
so I said, "What's that!?".

62
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:36,010
"I'm asking you what is this, punk?"

63
