after suffering 20 hours of pain.

75
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:13,920
But why do I still feel that I am alone?

76
00:04:14,940 --> 00:04:16,620
Jung-eun, why are you like this?

77
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,340
<i>What is this?</i>

78
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:21,230
I also know that you have suffered a lot.

79
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:25,140
Don't just know how I suffered.
Know my mother's sufferings, too.

80
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,440
<i>Of course, I know that.</i>

81
00:04:27,920 --> 00:04:29,140
