would she want to go?

88
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,670
If she'll go, who will take care of Yoo-na?

89
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:50,320
Hey, it's not like she specializes
in taking care of two persons.

90
00:04:51,610 --> 00:04:54,540
Honestly speaking, she came to Seoul because of you.

91
00:04:55,140 --> 00:04:56,580
Don't you remember it?

92
