224
00:16:42,380 --> 00:16:45,490
As our manager was promoted,
he attaches great importance to leadership.

225
00:16:45,900 --> 00:16:48,300
So this time, please do seriously
the mentoring evaluation...

226
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:50,500
...of Shin So-hee as her mentor.

227
00:16:51,230 --> 00:16:55,760
Did you know that 50% of the project report
comes from the mentor's evaluation?

228
00:16:58,300 --> 00:16:58,980
Yes.

229
00:17:00,070 --> 00:17:00,920
Then, I'm leaving now.

230
00:17:03,010 --> 00:17:05,180
You're a strong person.

231
00:17:10,320 --> 00:17:11,870
Some people say when anyone gets a hard time,

232
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:13,830
weak people drink soju,

233
00:17:13,830 --> 00:17:15,960
and strong people take vitamins.

234
00:17:16,980 --> 00:17:19,050
You're really a strong-willed person.

235
00:17:20,430 --> 00:17:21,520
I respect you very much.

236
00:18:04,740 --> 00:18:06,100
<i>You'll come back late today?</i>

237
00:18:06,540 --> 00:18:07,940
<i>He went out this weekend,</i>

238
00:18:07,940 --> 00:18:09,940
<i>but no one was at home all day.</i>

239
00:18:10,320 --> 00:18:12,100
